Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.86,0:22:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切將盡在我的掌握之中……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.44,0:22:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以……
